  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">DTBU Tier I &amp; II</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Project is expected to have a high development impact in the following measurable areas:  1. Increasing credit availability to the SMEs.  2. Supporting job creation through providing long term financing to the SMEs. 3. Growth in bank&apos;&apos;s profitability, which is expected to be achieved through strengthening DTBU&apos;&apos;s capital base, resulting in higher taxes to the Government. 5. Demonstration effect/market transformation through DTBU&apos;&apos;s continued lending to the target segment beyond the life of the Project.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The total project cost and proposed IFC investment is $5 million. IFC will finance the above amount in the form of a Subordinated Loan that qualifies for Tier II capital.  The above Subordinated Loan will be utilized to: (i) strengthen Diamond Trust Bank Uganda Limiteds (DTBU) capital base; and (ii) assist in DTBUs expansion of its lending activities to the SMEs.</narrative>
  </description>
